item.title: CVE-2017-5681|2024-08-05T15:11:48.289Z -- intel -- intel%20quick%20assist%20technology
item.description: The RSA-CRT implementation in the Intel QuickAssist Technology (QAT) Engine for OpenSSL versions prior to 0.5.19 may allow remote attackers to obtain private RSA keys by conducting a Lenstra side-channel attack.
